  <brief_title>Biomarkers and Therapeutic Modelisation in Heart Failure</brief_title>
  <acronym>BIOMIC</acronym>
  <official_title>Home-based Assessment of Plasma Volume, Serum Potassium and Renal Function Variations in Patients With Heart Failure and Low Left Ventricular Ejection Fraction: Pilot Study BIOMIC. Biomarkers and Therapeutic Modelisation in Heart Failure</official_title>
